Accuport is a platform that provides marine onboard chemical test solutions
we need to fetch all the available data from labcom database and then format it a bit to store into a sqlite database (accubase.sqlite)
we need to create a python program to that effect.
for every vessel there will be a diffent auth token and labcom account




Enhanced Tables:

  1. SAMPLING_POINTS - Added activity tracking and location info
  2. PARAMETERS - Added ideal ranges, category, and criticality levels
  3. MEASUREMENTS - Major enhancements:
    - String + numeric value storage
    - Quality control fields (ideal_status, ideal_low/high)
    - Operator and device tracking
    - Data validation flags
    - Multiple indexes for performance

  New Tables:

  4. ALERTS - Automatic out-of-range detection
    - 7 alerts automatically generated from MV October data
    - Tracks TOO LOW, TOO HIGH, CRITICAL conditions
    - Acknowledgment and resolution workflow
  5. PARAMETER_LIMITS - Custom limits per sampling point
    - Three-tier thresholds (ideal/warning/critical)
    - Time-based limits support
  6. FETCH_LOGS - Enhanced with detailed statistics

