  cd src
  python fetch_and_store.py mv_october 30

  # Or for other vessels
  python fetch_and_store.py mv_racer 60
  python fetch_and_store.py mt_aqua 30

  üí° Key Benefits

  1. Automatic Quality Monitoring - Alerts generated instantly for out-of-range values
  2. Full Traceability - Know who tested what, when, and with which device
  3. Flexible Data Storage - Handles both string and numeric values
  4. Performance Optimized - Strategic indexes on frequently queried fields
  5. Future-Ready - Supports custom limits and time-based ranges

  The enhanced schema is now production-ready and tested with real Labcom data! All 4 vessels (MV October, M.V Racer,
   MT Aqua, MT Voyager) can now be fetched and stored with comprehensive quality control tracking.
